as long as they continued to be of his mind
,
and no longer; for he was a very
pragmatical
fort of a fellow, and loved to have
his own way in every thing. This was the
cause
of a quarrel between him and
Roger
Carrier
, for it happened that Roger had
taken a fancy to dip his head into water,
[14]
[14]
Anabaptists
.
as the
most
