were
some
who envied the
steward
his
reputation, and
raised
stories
to his
disadvantage
,
which highly affronted him. At
K
this time Mr. Bull was
so
much off his
guard, as to give heed to
these
reports,
and take a
rash
step
in a hurry, which he
had
